{{see|dorruðr}}
==Old Norse==

===Noun===
'''Dọr-r-uð-r'''
# [[speer]]-[[fighter]] (a [[kenning]] for [[Odin]])

===Usage notes===
When used to refer to any generic speer-fighter (that is, when not used as a kenning for Odin), the inital letter of the word is not majuscule : [[dorruðr]].

